{"tid":504808,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"【真人真事改篇】【校園】【視覺小說】【日更二至三話】《雙妹嘜二八記事》","createTime":"2017-12-20T12:21:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T13:14:21.000Z","uid":92035,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b549e635f03af855c23775daf50bb2b22a154846","tid":504808,"uid":92035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:21:55.000Z","msg":"小弟參加咗Oice舉辦嘅視覺小說比賽，七月中用佢平台膽粗粗寫咗個故仔。基本上用自己嘅中學生涯改篇，有啲咁多奇幻，不過真係好少奇幻元素。<br />\n<br />\n本來係用正體中文寫，不過自己嗰陣就玩粵語梗，結果依家逼住全粵語。正體中文會一月打後補返。<br />\n<br />\n啲人物都係我自己畫，係唔多得。雖然比賽係月底31號deadline，我都打算一月十幾日Sembreak臨摹學畫靚啲，就算比賽完咗都繼續更新。<br />\n<br />\n由於係參賽作品，希望各位巴打可以down佢個App，碌落少少比個「心心」呢個故。<br />\n<br />\nOice係收費平台，我join得都係打算靠創作搵食，唔做Tuns去整㗎，依家反而有出無入&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n仲有想請咁多位巴打畀啲意見評下個故仔寫成點，自己好驚自high但寫得衰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/195200_e00dbbea07f2ab0e41b08bc43dee2d72.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F195200_e00dbbea07f2ab0e41b08bc43dee2d72.png&h=d223193c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n記得開聲，靜音會miss咗好多嘢。<br />\n<br />\n序章　第一話　吊詭的相遇：<a href=\"https://oice.com/story/3aa90d95cdfa4d01a0675a4508f312d7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2F3aa90d95cdfa4d01a0675a4508f312d7&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=54915fe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/3aa90d95cdfa4d01a0675a4508f312d7</a><br />\n序章舖敘。人手問題，只有第一集有選擇肢玩下，不過可以順住個選擇估女主角（妹）諗緊咩。<br />\n<br />\n第一章　第二話　一擔砂糖一升血：<br />\n<a href=\"https://oice.com/story/26bcd1eedc974318b3e39c119ed55c4f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2F26bcd1eedc974318b3e39c119ed55c4f&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=ec80abe2\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/26bcd1eedc974318b3e39c119ed55c4f</a><br />\n家姐出場，佢係最後一個畫嘅角色，應該係最順眼。由於我畫個陣唔記得縮返個胸，變咗勁大波。不過算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n第一章　第三話　班際旅行：<br />\n<a href=\"https://oice.com/story/c0c3e7637e81462aa9b2c094dbe65bf1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2Fc0c3e7637e81462aa9b2c094dbe65bf1&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=58c9fb28\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/c0c3e7637e81462aa9b2c094dbe65bf1</a><br />\n少少咸，考DSE嘅應該get到。<br />\n<br />\n推介一下另外兩個高質參賽作品，分別係《Revocation》同《Freelancer》。<br />\n<br />\n《Revocation》啲畫屈晒機，白髮蘿做主角。設計到似遊戲多過小說，仲有CG睇。<br />\n<a href=\"https://oice.com/story/a8d0a64c721d47f88a8cff708a5b910a?_branch_match_id=471980786420353961\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2Fa8d0a64c721d47f88a8cff708a5b910a%3F_branch_match_id%3D471980786420353961&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=734c8927\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/a8d0a64c721d47f88a8cff708a5b910a?_branch_match_id=471980786420353961</a><br />\n<br />\n《Freelancer》FB page：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ffreelancerbythunderrush%2F&d=L%2FuTO2Xyn%2BKc934WAUEEI%2FM6KyiA14vjm6WlJCMZo68%3D&h=feb3fda5\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/freelancerbythunderrush/</a><br />\n<br />\n小弟得一自己條友，畫面完成度真係比唔上以上兩Team<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21e9caef24987c7ed6af8dc8c1e21ef4a2924f2a","tid":504808,"uid":92035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:43:26.000Z","msg":"補充多句，成個故事我會一條條Link咁放晒上嚟，唔會話唔課畀我就睇唔到結局。<br />\n<br />\n點都畀啲意見呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4e5241338ddf0070516134f632bfa4883b4c1b","tid":504808,"uid":92035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T13:14:21.000Z","msg":"手機嘅話應該要down咗Oice app先開到"}]}